{"seriesId":312168,"title":"SPY×FAMILY","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/40288889/40288889.18340242","descriptionFirst":"西国(ウェスタリス)情報局対東課〈WISE(ワイズ)〉は諜報員(エージェント)〈黄昏(たそがれ)〉に、東国(オスタニア)で戦争計画を進めるデズモンドの調査を命じる。〈黄昏(たそがれ)〉は精神科医ロイド・フォージャーに扮し、標的と接触できる名門イーデン校に子供を入学させるため孤児のアーニャを引き取る。実はアーニャは他人の心を読む超能力者だった。ある日、〈黄昏(たそがれ)〉を狙うマフィア組織にアーニャが連れ去られてしまう。ロイドは任務の仕切り直しを考えるが……。\n\nロイド・フォージャー:江口拓也／アーニャ・フォージャー:種﨑敦美／ヨル・フォージャー:早見沙織\n\n原作:遠藤達哉（集英社「少年ジャンプ＋」連載）／監督:古橋一浩／製作会社:WIT STUDIO×CloverWorks／音楽:(K)NoW_NAME／キャラクターデザイン:嶋田和晃\n\n©遠藤達哉／集英社・SPY×FAMILY製作委員会\n\n次話→so40319505","tags":["少年ジャンプ","2022年春アニメ","Cパートあり","SPY×FAMILY_Dアニ_1⇔2⇔劇場版⇔3","アクション/バトル"],"cours":"2022-春","colKey":"さ","relatedSeries":[{"seriesId":434600,"title":"SPY×FAMILY Season 2","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/42851510/42851510.26399873"},{"seriesId":533578,"title":"SPY×FAMILY Season 3","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45472388/45472388.11228238"}],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so40288889","episodeNo":1,"title":"SPY×FAMILY　【MISSION：1】　オペレーション〈梟（ストリクス）〉","viewCounter":229193,"commentCounter":7965,"mylistCounter":2362,"lengthSeconds":1449,"startTime":"2022-04-09T23:30:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/40288889/40288889.18340242"},{"contentId":"so40319505","episodeNo":2,"title":"SPY×FAMILY　【MISSION：2】　妻役を確保せよ","viewCounter":206661,"commentCounter":10268,"mylistCounter":284,"lengthSeconds":1450,"startTime":"2022-04-16T23:30:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/40319505/40319505.29797602"},{"contentId":"so40355041","episodeNo":3,"title":"SPY×FAMILY　【MISSION：3】　受験対策をせよ","viewCounter":186274,"commentCounter":8340,"mylistCounter":232,"lengthSeconds":1450,"startTime":"2022-04-23T23:30:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/40355041/40355041.54333395"},{"contentId":"so40386219","episodeNo":4,"title":"SPY×FAMILY　【MISSION：4】　名門校面接試験","viewCounter":174351,"commentCounter":10075,"mylistCounte